This project builds on NVIDIA's open models:
  - nvidia/NVIDIA-Nemotron-3-Super-120B-A12B  (the speculative-decoding target)
  - nvidia/Nemotron-Labs-Diffusion-3B          (the drafter base)

The trained LoRA adapter and the self-distilled dataset produced by this project
are DERIVATIVE WORKS of those models and are therefore additionally governed by
the NVIDIA Open Model License under which the base models are released. Users of
the adapter/dataset must comply with that license in addition to Apache-2.0 for
the code. See:
  https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/agreements/enterprise-software/nvidia-open-model-license/

